eu.ehri.project.importers.base

Interface ItemImporter<I,T extends Accessible>

  • Type Parameters:
    I - Type of node representation that can be imported, for example, Map<String, Object>.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractImporter, CsvAuthoritativeItemImporter, CsvConceptImporter, CsvHistoricalAgentImporter, EacImporter, EadImporter, EagImporter, PersonalitiesImporter, UkrainianUnitImporter, VirtualEadImporter, Wp2PersonalitiesImporter

    public interface ItemImporter<I,T extends Accessible>
    Interface for importers that import documentary units, historical agents and virtual collections, with their constituent logical data, description(s), and date periods.
